005 年现场表演" decoding="async" loading="lazy" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/Kano-Ghetto-black-british-music-v-and-a-east-museum-exhibition.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/Kano-Ghetto-black-british-music-v-and-a-east-museum-exhibition-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/Kano-Ghetto-black-british-music-v-and-a-east-museum-exhibition-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/Kano-Ghetto-black-british-music-v-and-a-east-museum-exhibition-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/Kano-Ghetto-black-british-music-v-and-a-east-museum-exhibition-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/Kano-Ghetto-black-british-music-v-and-a-east-museum-exhibition-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /></p><p> V&amp;A 东博物馆将推出庆祝英国黑人音乐的展览。</p><p><strong>阅读更多：<a href="https://www.nme.com/blogs/dave-brit-awards-2020-black-boris-johnson-2612907">戴夫在英国队——他在《黑人》中的灼热表演如何对抗这个国家每一个种族主义者</a></strong></p><p><em>《音乐是黑人：英国故事》</em>将收录当代黑人英国音乐人（包括<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/little-simz">Little Simz</a> 、 <a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/stormzy">Stormzy</a>和<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/jorja-smith">Jorja Smith）</a>的新作品和<a href="https://www.nme.com/tag/bbc">BBC</a>档案材料。</p><p>展览中将展示跨越几代人的配乐以及“令人回味的”布景设计，该展览描绘了从塞缪尔·柯勒律治-泰勒到后来的世纪明星<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/sade">萨德</a>、<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/joan-armatrading">琼·阿玛特拉丁</a>和<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/tricky">特里奇</a>等 20 世纪初的先驱者对英国音乐文化的影响。</p><p> V&amp;A 东博物馆预计于 2025 年开放，是南肯辛顿维多利亚和阿尔伯特博物馆 (V&amp;A) 的最新分支，后者是世界著名的博物馆，由维多利亚女王和阿尔伯特亲王于 1852 年创立。 </p><figure id="attachment_3527973" aria-describedby="caption-attachment-3527973" style="width: 2000px" class="wp-caption alignnone"><img decoding="async" loading="lazy" class="wp-image-3527973 size-full" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/dennis-morris-black-british-music-v-and-a-east-museum-exhibition.jpg" alt="1974 年的照片显示东伦敦哈克尼 Aces 俱乐部内的两名男子" width="2000" height="1270" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/dennis-morris-black-british-music-v-and-a-east-museum-exhibition.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/dennis-morris-black-british-music-v-and-a-east-museum-exhibition-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/dennis-morris-black-british-music-v-and-a-east-museum-exhibition-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/dennis-morris-black-british-music-v-and-a-east-museum-exhibition-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/dennis-morris-black-british-music-v-and-a-east-museum-exhibition-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/dennis-morris-black-british-music-v-and-a-east-museum-exhibition-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /><figcaption id="caption-attachment-3527973" class="wp-caption-text"> 1974 年的照片显示东伦敦哈克尼 Aces 俱乐部内的两名男子。图片来源：丹尼斯·莫里斯，《王牌俱乐部，雪莉伯爵音响系统，哈克尼》，1974 年（拍摄），2010 年（印刷）<br /> © Dennis Morris 由伦敦维多利亚和阿尔伯特博物馆提供</figcaption></figure><p>近年来，维多利亚与阿尔伯特博物馆 (V&amp;A Dundee) 不断扩张，邓迪维多利亚与阿尔伯特博物馆 (V&amp;A Dundee) 最近开业。贝斯纳尔·格林 (Bethnal Green) 的 The Young V&amp;A 博物馆也于 6 月重新开放。</p><p>其即将进行的扩建位于斯特拉特福伊丽莎白女王奥林匹克公园东岸地区，这里是一个新的艺术、创新和教育中心的所在地。这是伦敦市长耗资 11 亿英镑的奥运遗产项目的一部分。 </p><figure id="attachment_3527985" aria-describedby="caption-attachment-3527985" style="width: 2000px" class="wp-caption alignnone"><img decoding="async" loading="lazy" class="size-full wp-image-3527985" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/little-simz-black-british-music-v-and-a-east-museum-exhibition.jpg" alt="小西姆兹" width="2000" height="1270" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/little-simz-black-british-music-v-and-a-east-museum-exhibition.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/little-simz-black-british-music-v-and-a-east-museum-exhibition-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/little-simz-black-british-music-v-and-a-east-museum-exhibition-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/little-simz-black-british-music-v-and-a-east-museum-exhibition-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/little-simz-black-british-music-v-and-a-east-museum-exhibition-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/little-simz-black-british-music-v-and-a-east-museum-exhibition-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /><figcaption id="caption-attachment-3527985" class="wp-caption-text">小西姆兹。图片来源：“Little Simz 于 2022 年 2 月 8 日在英国伦敦 O2 体育馆举行的 2022 年全英音乐奖颁奖典礼上表演”<br />摄影：Karwai Tang/WireImage</figcaption></figure><p> V&amp;A 东博物馆将坐落在公园对面，靠近 V&amp;A 东仓库，该馆将为游客提供身临其境的幕后体验，欣赏 V&amp;A 藏品。</p><p> <em>《音乐是黑人：一个英国故事》的</em>策展人获得了前所未有的访问 BBC 展览档案的权限；这种自由帮助创作了跨越几代人和不同流派的配乐，从说唱、回响贝斯到非洲节奏和污垢。 </p><figure id="attachment_3527980" aria-describedby="caption-attachment-3527980" style="width: 2000px" class="wp-caption alignnone"><img decoding="async" loading="lazy" class="size-full wp-image-3527980" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/Kano-Ghetto-black-british-music-v-and-a-east-museum-exhibition.jpg" alt="Kano 和 Ghetto 于 2005 年现场表演" width="2000" height="1270" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/Kano-Ghetto-black-british-music-v-and-a-east-museum-exhibition.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/Kano-Ghetto-black-british-music-v-and-a-east-museum-exhibition-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/Kano-Ghetto-black-british-music-v-and-a-east-museum-exhibition-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/Kano-Ghetto-black-british-music-v-and-a-east-museum-exhibition-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/Kano-Ghetto-black-british-music-v-and-a-east-museum-exhibition-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/Kano-Ghetto-black-british-music-v-and-a-east-museum-exhibition-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /><figcaption id="caption-attachment-3527980" class="wp-caption-text">图片来源：Sam White，“卡诺和贫民窟，iD Live，Cargo，2005 年 3 月”<br /> ©萨姆·怀特</figcaption></figure><figure id="attachment_3527982" aria-describedby="caption-attachment-3527982" style="width: 2000px" class="wp-caption alignnone"><img decoding="async" loading="lazy" class="size-full wp-image-3527982" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/tricky-black-british-music-v-and-a-east-museum-exhibition.jpg" alt="Trip-hop 先驱 Tricky" width="2000" height="1270" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/tricky-black-british-music-v-and-a-east-museum-exhibition.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/tricky-black-british-music-v-and-a-east-museum-exhibition-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/tricky-black-british-music-v-and-a-east-museum-exhibition-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/tricky-black-british-music-v-and-a-east-museum-exhibition-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/tricky-black-british-music-v-and-a-east-museum-exhibition-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/tricky-black-british-music-v-and-a-east-museum-exhibition-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /><figcaption id="caption-attachment-3527982" class="wp-caption-text"> Trip-hop 先驱 Tricky。图片来源：Adrian Boot，《Tricky》，2006 © Adrian Boot，urbanimage.tv</figcaption></figure><p>该展览将探讨英国黑人音乐背后的社会、历史和文化背景，探讨它如何导致其他未提及的英国流派的创造，包括 2 音、丛林、拉格、鼓&#39;n&#39;贝斯、旅行跳、英国车库、钻头等等。</p><p>绘画、印刷品、海报、海报、雕塑、电视、时尚、纺织品、摄影和电影都将有助于讲述英国黑人音乐的更广泛的故事及其超越声音的文化影响。</p><p>作为展览的一部分，V&amp;A East 委托<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/j-hus">J Hus</a> 、 <a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/pa-salieu">Pa Salieu</a>和<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/kojey-radical">Kojey Radical</a>音乐录影带的导演组合 Meeks &amp; Frost 拍摄了一部新电影，并于今天（11 月 1 日）发布了新的预告片。请看下面。 </p><p><iframe loading="lazy" title="音乐是黑色的：一个英国故事 | V&amp;A 东博物馆将于 2025 年开幕" width="696" height="392" src="https://www.youtube.com/embed/Fm9_we84_ZA?feature=oembed" frameborder="0" allow="accelerometer; autoplay; clipboard-write; encrypted-media; gyroscope; picture-in-picture; web-share" allowfullscreen></iframe></p><p>此外，作为 V&amp;A East 开幕式的一部分，BBC、Sadlers Wells East、UAL 伦敦时装学院和 UCL East 将联手探索展览主题，在伊丽莎白女王奥林匹克体育场举办一系列特别活动和表演公园。</p><p>传奇音乐人和 BBC 广播电台播音员<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/trevor-nelson">特雷弗·尼尔森 (Trevor Nelson)</a>表示：“英国出现了许多不同色彩和色调的黑人音乐，以及许多不拘一格的风格。事实上，我们还没有举办过关于英国黑人音乐的全国性展览，这让我感到非常惊讶。我觉得有必要记录下来。但更重要的是，讲述那些不为人知的故事。”</p><p>维多利亚与阿尔伯特博物馆<em>《音乐是黑人：一个英国故事</em>》策展人<em>兼非洲和侨民表演</em>策展人杰奎琳·施普林格表示：“音乐是我们生活的配乐，也是团结最有力的工具之一。当我们在节日和演出中背诵歌词、回忆童年卧室里完美的舞蹈动作、伴随着吉他伴奏、贝斯线下降和欢快的乐器演奏时，它给集体和个人带来了欢乐。</p><p> “在英国殖民主义和不断发展的社会、政治和文化景观的背景下，我们将庆祝黑人和英国黑人音乐作为抗议、肯定和创造力的工具的丰富性和多样性，并揭示一些背后不为人知的故事。世界上有史以来最流行的音乐。”</p><p>与此同时， <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/david-bowie-is-archive-to-be-made-into-permanent-uk-venue-by-va-3403195">V&amp;A 东博物馆将在 2025 年为 V&amp;A 的大卫·鲍伊 (David Bowie) 展览提供永久举办地</a>，此前该博物馆获得了包括 80,000 多件手写歌词、时尚单品、布景设计和奖项在内的大量档案。</p><p> <a rel="nofollow" href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/v-and-a-east-museum-london-to-open-with-exhibition-celebrating-black-british-music-3527914">伦敦 V&amp;A 东博物馆即将开幕，并举办庆祝英国黑人音乐的展览，该展览</a>首先出现在<a rel="nofollow" href="https://www.nme.com">NME</a>上。</p> ;
